{"word":"ἔθος","slug":"ἔθος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἔϑος, ους, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔθω\">ἔθω</a></el> ‘be accustomed’, from which <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἴωθα\">εἴωθα</a></el> is derived; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐθίζω\">ἐθίζω</a></el>] ‘a way of doing things marked by recurring procedure’, <b>custom, practice<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of usage established by tradition or legal definition <b><a href='B:490 1:9'>Lk 1:9</a>; <a href='B:490 2:42'>2:42</a>; <a href='B:500 19:40'>J 19:40</a>; <a href='B:510 6:14'>Ac 6:14</a>; <a href='B:510 15:1'>15:1</a>; <a href='B:510 21:21'>21:21</a>; <a href='B:510 25:16'>25:16</a>; <a href='B:510 26:3'>26:3</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of personal habit <b><a href='B:490 22:39'>Lk 22:39</a>; <a href='B:650 10:25'>Hb 10:25</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔθνος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔθου\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}